Name: Delicious Mountains, Sea, and Sky
Desc: A large platter with a mix of meat and vegetables. Thick, juicy chunks of meat have soaked up all the spices, mingling delightfully with the crispness of the fruit and vegetables on the tip of your tongue. Not only does it take your taste buds for a rollercoaster ride, but it leaves your stomach feeling satisfied too. No wonder this dish has so many loyal fans.
Effect: Decreases all party members' gliding and sprinting Stamina consumption by 25% for 900s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
